1390
01:04:07,053 --> 01:04:08,486
Uh...

1391
01:04:14,060 --> 01:04:16,221
Kate...

1392
01:04:16,262 --> 01:04:17,593
Uh, Kate!

1393
01:04:17,630 --> 01:04:19,154
