2222
01:50:23,086 --> 01:50:25,418
( clock chimes )

2223
01:50:30,460 --> 01:50:32,758
( clock chimes )

2224
01:50:37,001 --> 01:50:38,696
Charlie...

2225
01:50:40,805 --> 01:50:43,797
I'll love you forever.

2226
01:50:43,841 --> 01:50:46,935
Love you.

2227
01:50:49,514 --> 01:50:52,210
It's okay.

2228
01:50:55,686 --> 01:50:56,983
( clock chimes )

2229
